{"tid":1503539,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"The Chainsmokers港騷 歌迷爆粗鬧林鄭","createTime":"2019-08-25T04:11:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T04:16:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"02fcb3ed6851dacc7f38cbaf0686273b6dcceaa0","tid":1503539,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:11:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190825/20755336\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190825%2F20755336&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRULc0zXsqQl3D3Nzt16t%2FTIU%3D&h=da15b9a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190825%2F20755336&h=a9b4d482\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190825/20755336</a><br />\n<br />\nThe Chainsmokers港騷<br />\n歌迷爆粗鬧林鄭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190825/large/1566650970_50ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190825%2Flarge%2F1566650970_50ef.jpg&h=7ced67cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n演唱會尾聲，Drew興奮地跳到台下跟歌迷近距離接觸。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國電音組合The Chainsmokers繼去年3月首次來港舉行演唱會後，前晚再度駕臨香港，於機場亞洲國際博覽館舉行「World War Joy」巡迴演唱會，全場座無虛席。雖然遇上「香港之路」行動，但觀眾仍隔空支持行動，開場前在場內一同開着手機電筒，互相呼應大叫「香港人加油」、「光復香港 時代革命」等口號，之後更有歌迷爆粗大鬧行政長官林鄭月娥：「林鄭X你老X！」。<br />\n<br />\n主音Drew Taggart和琴手Alex Pall於8時45分正式出場，粉絲登時跟着拍子high爆舉手喪跳，暫將所有不快事拋諸腦後，Drew之後突然爆Seed大叫：「Welcome to the darkness！（歡迎來到黑暗）」Drew又表示再次來到香港演出感到非常興奮，未幾背後的LED螢幕播出一條由香港景色剪接而成的短片，令現場氣氛推至高峯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190825/large/1566650969_3bbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190825%2Flarge%2F1566650969_3bbc.jpg&h=1fa273c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nThe Chainsmokers前晚在亞博館開騷，演唱多首經典作品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190825/large/1566651222_bbaa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190825%2Flarge%2F1566651222_bbaa.jpg&h=53c34d43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDrew在演唱會上，不時拿出木結他伴奏。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n落台手牽手<br />\n<br />\n除了歌曲之間的拿手DJ混音演出外，The Chainsmokers共演唱14首耳熟能詳作品，包括《Don't let me down》、《Closer》和《Something just like this》等，Drew還多次拿起木結他伴奏，演出中亦加插音樂總監兼鼓手Matt McGuire的打鼓及Alex的鋼琴獨奏環節。演唱會尾聲，Drew興奮地跳到台下作近距離接觸，歌迷即把握機會與他手牽手，成功connect！Matt騷後也在Ig上載第一身角度短片，留言指當晚非常瘋狂，感謝港人令人讚嘆的正能量。<br />\n<br />\n採訪：黃思虎 <br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n基燮娶老婆預告四年後生B"},{"pid":"a4543d7b82cc8859d75d335a79e6d0f1116bc2f5","tid":1503539,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:14:04.000Z","msg":"借位 <br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7998bd89056b1ab914324cd3bc75a361c894347f","tid":1503539,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:16:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491396</a>"}]}